PassionOAS activate
    Events
        Unit - A unit Starts the effect of an ability
    Conditions
        (Ability being cast) Equal to Swordsaint: Passion of a Saint (Channel ON)
    Actions
        Set VariableSet PoaS_MUI1 = (PoaS_MUI1 + 1)
        -------- Dynamic indexing --------
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                PoaS_MUI1 Greater than PoaS_maxindex
            Then - Actions
                Set VariableSet PoaS_MUI2[PoaS_MUI1] = PoaS_MUI1
                Set VariableSet PoaS_maxindex = PoaS_MUI1
            Else - Actions
        -------- ai is for "anti-inconvenicence" (integer) --------
        Set VariableSet PoaS_ai = PoaS_MUI2[PoaS_MUI1]
        -------- Cast Setup --------
        Set VariableSet PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai] = (Triggering unit)
        -------- Buffer --------
        Set VariableSet PoaS_mana = (Mana of PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai])
        If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
            If - Conditions
                PoaS_mana Greater than or equal to 1.00
            Then - Actions
                Custom script:   set udg_PoaS_aoe[udg_PoaS_ai] = GetAbilityReal("aoe", udg_PoaS_caster[udg_PoaS_ai], getlvl(), 'A007')
                Custom script:   set udg_PoaS_dmg[udg_PoaS_ai] = GetAbilityReal("herodur", udg_PoaS_caster[udg_PoaS_ai], getlvl(), 'A007')
                Set VariableSet PoaS_dmg[PoaS_ai] = (PoaS_dmg[PoaS_ai] + (0.30 x (Real((Intelligence of PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai] (Include bonuses))))))
                Set VariableSet PoaS_dmg[PoaS_ai] = (PoaS_dmg[PoaS_ai] x 0.50)
                Unit - Add PassionOfASaint BuffAura (Endurance Dummy) to PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai]
                Unit - For PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai], Ability PassionOfASaint BuffAura (Endurance Dummy), Hide ability: True
                -------- speedboost --------
                Set VariableSet PoaS_tempp = (Position of PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai])
                Unit - Create 1 Dummy for (Owner of PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai]) at PoaS_tempp facing Default building facing degrees
                Set VariableSet PoaS_dummy = (Last created unit)
                Unit - Add PassionOfASaint MovementSpeed (Bloodlust) to PoaS_dummy
                Unit - Order PoaS_dummy to Orc Shaman - Bloodlust PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai]
                Unit - Add a 1.50 second Generic expiration timer to PoaS_dummy
                Custom script:   call RemoveLocation(udg_PoaS_tempp)
                -------- Active/deactive --------
                Unit - For PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai], Ability Swordsaint: Passion of a Saint (Channel ON), Hide ability: True
                Unit - For PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai], Ability Swordsaint: Passion of a Saint (Channel OFF), Hide ability: False
                Unit Group - Add PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai] to PoaS_activegroup
                -------- Visual setup --------
                Special Effect - Create a special effect attached to the origin of PoaS_caster[PoaS_ai] using HolyAura.mdx
                Set VariableSet PoaS_attach[PoaS_ai] = (Last created special effect)
                -------- begin looping --------
                If (All Conditions are True) then do (Then Actions) else do (Else Actions)
                    If - Conditions
                        (PassonOAS loop <gen> is on) Equal to False
                    Then - Actions
                        Trigger - Turn on PassonOAS loop <gen>
                    Else - Actions
            Else - Actions
                -------- Not enough mana --------
